title: praNamAmyaham
sahitya:
praNamAmyaham shrI gaurIsutam phaNitalpa vAsudEva sutam


anupallavi

  gaNanAtha mama brnda sEvitam phaNihAra bhUSitam munivara vanditam


caraNam    dhrta cAru mOdakam gajamukham sitakarAmita garva bhanjakam 
natabhUta santOSa dAyakam shrtabhakta pAlakam siddhivinAyakam
